&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;A Mid-Week Treat at the Races!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

Come and join us for an exceptional Tuesday afternoon at Wolverhampton Racecourse featuring high-action Flat racing and an incredible atmosphere.

Not to mention you can indulge in a variety of tasty on-the-go treats from one of our bars and eateries as you savour all the sights and sounds of live horse racing action. 

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt;A Social Occasion&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;

Gather your friends and family for a great value experience you won't want to miss. Nothing beats the thrill of watching horses whizz by as the crowd roars home their runner!

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;b&gt; Tickets&lt;/b&gt; &lt;/h2&gt;

Snap up a ticket for your desired enclosure to attend a unique day out at the races, don't forget you SAVE when you book in advance. 
Or if you're looking to make your day extra special, why not enjoy a three-course meal in the Horizons Restaurant with an exceptional view of the track for an unforgettable experience?

Where:  &lt;a href=&quot; https://goo.gl/maps/6esaoCsoz18VK6tR9 &quot;&gt; Get directions &lt;/a&gt;

